## 8. robots.txt Configuration

Update `src/app/robots.ts`:

```typescript
export default function robots(): MetadataRoute.Robots {
  const baseUrl =
    process.env.NEXT_PUBLIC_APP_URL || "https://client-domain.com";

  return {
    rules: [
      {
        userAgent: "*",
        allow: "/",
        disallow: [
          "/api/", // Protect API routes
          "/admin/", // Protect admin area
          "/dev/", // Hide dev tools
          "/private/", // Any private sections
        ],
      },
    ],
    sitemap: `${baseUrl}/sitemap.xml`,
  };
}
```

**For staging sites**, add:

```typescript
rules: [
  {
    userAgent: "*",
    disallow: "/",  // Block all search engines on staging
  },
],
```

