## Tips & Best Practices

### Communication with Client

**Before starting:**

- Request brand guidelines, logos, and color codes
- Ask for font preferences or licenses
- Get access to APIs and third-party services
- Clarify content approval process

**During development:**

- Send staging URL for feedback
- Document any deviations from spec
- Ask questions early to avoid rework

### Code Quality

- Keep client-specific code organized
- Document any unusual client requirements
- Use TypeScript for type safety
- Follow the project's existing patterns
- Write accessible, semantic HTML

### Performance

- Optimize images before adding them
- Use Next.js Image component
- Lazy load non-critical components
- Monitor bundle size
- Test on slower connections

